<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-107] docbook-&gt;pdf conversion makes tabs only one space</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-107</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like for conversion to pdf, the converter is making the tabs in &amp;lt;programlisting&amp;gt; blocks come out as only a single character.  The tabs look better in the html output.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is probably some XSL setting we can use to make tabs become 8 spaces (or the equivalent spacing) in the pdf conversion.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="16831">LUDOC-107</key>
            <summary>docbook-&gt;pdf conversion makes tabs only one space</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
                                            <priority id="4" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/priorities/minor.svg">Minor</priority>
                        <status id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/statuses/open.png" description="The issue is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.">Open</status>
                    <statusCategory id="2" key="new" colorName="default"/>
